Classes.Filters

Class FilterSet<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • Classes.Filters.FilterSet<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - Type the Filter should be applied to.
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    EntryCounterFilterSet, LetterCounterFilterSet, TypeCounterFilterSet

    public class FilterSet<T>
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents a set of Filters. A Set of Filters may be applied to an -Item or Collection collectively.
